        "Id": "4fc4ac38-e4d6-4e2e-b0aa-d4a9ca49d517",
        "Type": "usercreated",
        "Title": "Key Party - The Uninvited",
        "Location": "LOCATION_ANCESTRAL_BULLDOG",
        "PublicId": "128972933438",
        "ScenePath": "assembly:/_pro/scenes/missions/Ancestral/scene_bulldog.entity",
        "TileImage": "$($repository 0f88cdaa-d784-4951-8696-ea3065cc6228).Image",
        "Description": "Now that all of the staff at Dartmoor are fully vaccinated, they want to party like it’s 1975, with a swingin’ key party. Not everyone is invited, though. Eliminate anyone over 35 who has a key to ensure that they don’t crash the party and ruin everyone’s fun. Try not to hurt the staff, as they pooled their meager earnings to fund this contract.\r\rI’ll leave you to prepare.",
